@startuml
title ML / Biometric Processing Pipeline

skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #FDFEFE
  BorderColor     #2C3E50
  FontSize 12
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FEF9E7
  BorderColor     #F0B27A
}

|Camera (CameraX)|
start
:Capture ImageProxy frame;

|FaceAnalyzer|
:Convert ImageProxy\nto Bitmap;
:ML Kit Face Detection\n(landmarks · classifications · tracking);

if (Face detected?) then (no face\nor multiple)
  :Emit feedback state\n(NoFace / MultipleFaces);
  stop
endif

:FaceValidation\n──────────────\n• Face centered in oval\n• Size >= 80% of guide\n• Head rotation <= 12°\n• Eye landmarks detectable\n• Eyes open prob >= 0.70\n• Movement speed <= 2000 px/s;

if (Geometry valid?) then (no)
  :Emit feedback state\n(CenterFace / MoveCloser /\nLookStraight / HoldStill /\nEyesNotOpen);
  stop
endif

|FaceAttributeClassifier (TFLite)|
note right
  Runs every 500 ms
  MobileNetV2 · input 96×96
  Outputs: glasses prob, hat prob
  Threshold: >= 0.6 → reject
end note
:Classify face attributes\n(glasses · hat);

if (Attributes OK?) then (no)
  :Emit feedback state\n(WearingGlasses / WearingHat);
  stop
endif

|LivenessDetector (ONNX Runtime)|
note right
  Runs every 500 ms
  SilentFace ×2 models (scale 2.7 · 4.0)
  Input 80×80 · averaged scores
  Threshold: >= 0.972017 → live
end note
:Passive liveness check\n(SilentFace dual-scale);

if (Live face?) then (no)
  :Emit feedback state\n(SpoofDetected);
  stop
endif

|FaceSampleCollector|
:Align face crop via\neye landmark geometry\n(target: 112×112 px);
:Laplacian variance\nblur check >= 220;

if (Sharp frame?) then (no)
  :Emit feedback state\n(ImproveFocus);
  stop
endif

:Buffer aligned sample\n(100 ms between samples);

if (4 samples collected?) then (no)
  :Emit FaceDetected\n(continue loop);
  stop
endif

:Return 4 aligned bitmaps;

|MobileFaceNetLiteRT (TFLite)|
note right
  Input: 112×112 RGB
  Normalise: (px − 127.5) / 128.0
  Output: 128-d float vector
  CPU inference
end note
:Extract 128-d embedding\nper sample (×4);
:Average 4 embeddings\n→ L2 normalise\n→ final embedding vector;

|FaceRecognizerViewModel|
if (Flow mode?) then (ENROLL)
  :Store pending embedding\n→ navigate to name entry;
else (VERIFY)
  :Cosine similarity vs\nall stored embeddings\n(VerifyUserUseCase);
  if (Best score >= 0.82?) then (yes)
    :Navigate → Verify Success;
  else (no)
    :Navigate → Verify Failed;
  endif
endif

stop

@enduml
